  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kempner didn't know what the charge was against him, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you know a certain [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was this German journalist that they had gotten the notebook or the thing out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this got to be an international dispute between Switzerland-- praise heaven there's a Switzerland-- between Switzerland and the German government.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Hitler said, that's too hot to hold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let those men out of prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Switzerland was going to go to the international governments and appeal this case.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How could a person be kidnapped down the streets of Basel and taken to Germany and put in--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- they wanted the whole thing quashed-- no trial.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Switzerland brought so much pressure to bear on the German government that they quashed the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they let Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner out, but he had no more appetite to stay out in business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And very shortly after that, he went to Florence, Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went to Florence, Italy, in order to have a school there for German children that Jewish children that couldn't go to German school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a period of his life there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
